      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td class="nav">&lt;nav&gt</td>
        <td>Navigation</td>
        <td>This is used to identify the navigation of a site, ex. Home, About, Contact, etc.</td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td class="main">&lt;main&gt</td>
        <td>Main</td>
        <td>The Main is used to identify the subject of the page, such as body, etc.</td>
